{"ProductId":"25","Title":"Reserve<sup class='symbolstxt'>®</sup> Wood Modern","ShortDescription":"Clean lines and simple forms invite the beauty of natural wood stand out","Description":"","ThumbnailImage":null,"ShowcaseImage":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/images/default-source/product-images/showcase-images/reserve-modern-design-cladding-solid-garage-door-595.webp?sfvrsn=b04b7a7a_9","CanonicalUrl":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/reserve-modern-contemporary-garage-doors","Overview":"<h3>Modern Style, Real Wood Warmth</h3><h4>Premium 4-Layer Build</h4><p>Each door combines natural wood cladding, a sturdy base core, polystyrene insulation, and a smooth wood backer for long-lasting strength and energy efficiency.</p><h4>Custom Looks, Your Way</h4><p>Pick from seven sleek designs and six gorgeous wood species plus optional windows or metal accent strips. Finish it off with paint, stain, or choose from over 1,500 <a href=\"https://www.clopaydoor.com/residential/buyingguide/colorblast\">Color Blast&reg; custom colors</a>.</p><h4>Energy-Smart Insulation</h4><p><a href=\"https://www.clopaydoor.com/residential/buyingguide/garage-door-materials/insulation\">Polystyrene insulation</a> (R-value 5.9) keeps your garage more comfortable, no matter the weather.</p><h4>Built for the Elements</h4><p>Add Clopay&rsquo;s WindCode&reg; reinforcement for extra strength in areas prone to high winds.</p><h4>Environmental Assurance</h4><p>Clopay doors are compliant with environmental laws and regulations. Clopay doors do not contain HFCs. All Clopay doors are compliant with:</p><ul><li>California SB 1013</li><li>Washington HB 1112 &ndash; Hydrofluorocarbon Greenhouse Gas Emissions</li><li>Canadian regulations amending the ozone-depleting substances and halocarbon alternatives regulations</li><li>New Jersey A-5583/S-3919 &ndash; Greenhouse Gas Bill</li></ul>","Options":"","Construction":"<h3>How It&rsquo;s Made: Reserve&reg; Wood Modern</h3><p>Every Reserve&reg; Wood Modern garage door is engineered for durability and style. At its core, you&rsquo;ll find a solid Hemlock wood frame packed with polystyrene insulation to boost energy efficiency and block out the elements. On the outside, beautiful wood cladding gives each door its unique character, while a Luan wood backer adds an extra layer of strength and a clean interior finish.</p><p>Durable hardware, including heavy-duty hinges, rollers, and track, keeps your door running smoothly and quietly. For added protection, an optional vinyl weather seal (in a rust-resistant aluminum retainer) helps keep out drafts and moisture, guarding your garage from the elements. Each door also features Clopay&rsquo;s patented Safe-T-Bracket&reg;, designed to prevent injuries when the door is under tension.</p><img src=\"https://www.clopaydoor.com/images/default-source/product-images/construction/cutaway-reserve-wood-modern.webp?sfvrsn=6e970bbc_2\" alt=\"Reserve Wood Modern\" sf-size=\"100\" /><ol><li>Cladding</li><li>Base Material</li><li>Polystyrene Insulated Hemlock Frame</li><li>Luan Inside Skin</li></ol>","Models":"","FeaturesBenefits":"","SpringsHardware":"","GroupName":"","H1HeaderTitle":"Reserve Wood Modern","DisplayIndex":17,"ImageGallery":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/image-gallery/reserve-wood-modern","ColorDisclaimer":"<p>Your Reserve&reg; Wood Modern garage door is available in a beautiful range of stain colors designed to bring out the natural character of the wood. Choose from classics like Natural, Natural Oak, Cedar, Teak, Butternut, Mahogany, and Dark Oak for rich, authentic tones that highlight the wood&rsquo;s unique grain.</p><p>For a more dramatic, modern look, select Dark Oak Ebony Wash or Ebony Wash &mdash; two deep, bold finishes that make a statement. All stain colors are carefully formulated to complement the door&rsquo;s real wood construction, enhancing texture and depth for stunning curb appeal.</p><p><em>Clopay stain colors shown on Cedar wood. Note: Color may vary from on screen. Custom colors are available.</em></p>","TopSectionDisclaimer":"","HardwareDisclaimer":"","DesignDisclaimer":"<p>With the Reserve&reg; Wood Modern garage door, you can choose from striking offset window patterns, where a mix of short and long glass panels brings in natural light with a contemporary edge. If you love contrast, accent strip designs feature sleek aluminum flush strips set between wood planks, creating eye-catching lines and a hint of flair.</p><p>If you prefer something a bit more streamlined, go for the horizontal cladding design. You&rsquo;ll get classic wood planks arranged in full or alternating lengths for a clean, minimalist look. Many designs are available in both right-hand and left-hand configurations, so you can tailor the look to your home&rsquo;s architecture. For doors up to 10 feet wide, ask about seamless &ldquo;no splice&rdquo; options for an uninterrupted appearance.</p><p><em>*Design is available right hand and left hand.<br />**Unspliced models are only available up to 10' wide.</em></p>","RelatedProducts":[{"Title":"Modern Steel™","ImageUrl":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/images/default-source/product-images/showcase-images/modern-steel-flush_fullview-window-black-garage-door-595.webp?sfvrsn=db7014e9_14","Id":"170","Url":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/modern-steel-collection","DisplayIndex":7,"ShortDescription":"Subtle modern beauty, simple up-keep","AlternativeText":"Modern Steel"},{"Title":"Avante<sup class='symbolstxt'>®</sup> – Now Available with C-Power™ Technology","ImageUrl":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/images/default-source/product-images/showcase-images/tnahcpower01showcase.webp?sfvrsn=e1a1ed6c_1","Id":"16","Url":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/avante","DisplayIndex":9,"ShortDescription":"Aluminum and glass doors that make your garage a stunning focal point, providing natural light by day and a dramatic glow at night","AlternativeText":"Avante"},{"Title":"Classic™ Steel","ImageUrl":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/images/default-source/product-images/showcase-images/classicsteel-ironoreshowcase.webp?sfvrsn=25b7a514_1","Id":"13","Url":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/classic","DisplayIndex":19,"ShortDescription":"Strength and durability in a wide range of looks and colors, so you never have to sacrifice style","AlternativeText":"Classic Steel"}],"ProductBrochures":[{"Title":"Wood Idea Book","ImageUrl":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/images/default-source/brochures/rsdr-woodidea-10.webp?sfvrsn=e62fe2df_5","Type":"Brochure","Url":"https://literature.clopay.com/pdf_files/RSDR-WOODIDEA-10.pdf","Extension":"PDF","DisplayIndex":1}],"ProductInstallationAndCare":[{"Title":"Installation Instructions for Wood Garage Doors","ImageUrl":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/images/default-source/installation-instructions/installmanual-wood.webp?sfvrsn=dfa1869e_2","Type":"Instruction Manual","Url":"https://literature.clopay.com/pdf_files/INST-4150079_EN.pdf","Extension":"PDF","DisplayIndex":1},{"Title":"Wood Care and Maintenance","ImageUrl":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/images/default-source/care-and-maintenance/cmb-4150088_en.webp?sfvrsn=de832edf_3","Type":"Finish & Care","Url":"https://literature.clopay.com/pdf_files/CMB-4150088_EN.pdf","Extension":"PDF","DisplayIndex":2},{"Title":"Installation Warranty","ImageUrl":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/images/default-source/warranty/cbpc-madadgdinstallwarranty1yr-15.webp?sfvrsn=99c1bfdc_4","Type":"Warranty","Url":"https://literature.clopay.com/pdf_files/CBPC-MADADGDINSTALLWARRANTY1YR-15.pdf","Extension":"PDF","DisplayIndex":3},{"Title":"Handle Installation for Modern Series","ImageUrl":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/images/default-source/installation-instructions/installmanual-modernseries.webp?sfvrsn=de9b6a61_2","Type":"Instruction Manual","Url":"https://literature.clopay.com/pdf_files/INST-0137446_EN.pdf","Extension":"PDF","DisplayIndex":4}],"ProductImageGallery":[{"IsImage":true,"ImageUrl":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/images/default-source/product-images/garage-doors/reservewoodmodern/normal/reserve-modern-des